== Parsing the damage...<br>
============================<br>
<br>
33,767 total nuke damage.<br>
25 mana nukes (4 crits)<br>
3 boot nukes<br>
<br>
Ending time: 1:25:31<br>
Starting Time: 1:18:46<br>
<br>
Total fight time: 6 min 45 sec<br>
<br>
Average Nuke DPS for the fight: 33767/405= 83.375 DPS<br>
<br>
Estimated pet DPS: 65 DPS<br>
Total estimated pet damage: 65*405= 26,325<br>
I'm confident in the DPS I estimated here, we have fought Treah other times and I stepped into melee and saw procs going off, DS doing it's work, and Epic pet landing tons of hits for high damage.<br>
<br>
25 nukes of Shock of Fiery Blades<br>
SoFB = 334 mana -10% specialization Conj -10% Mana Preservation III -15% Spell casting Mastery 3<br>
X = 334 - 33.4 - 33.4 - 50.1<br>
X = 217.1 mana per cast (average)<br>
25x217.1 = 5427.5 mana spent total<br>
<br>
