The mobs name is NOT &quot;Treant,&quot; in PoN.  <br>
<br>
Why would mages make things up when it is as clear as you see it traveling down the side wall of PoN.<br>
<br>
charming Enchanters, charming Druids, a group here or there.<br>
<br>
If its not already grossly shown already.  The trees there do not cast spells.  They are a meleeing class mob.  They do kick and they do bash.  Finally, even 2-3 mage pets are pale in comparison to a charmed PoP pet.  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>A hasted charmed PoP is often greater than a raiding group.  At least some of you know, seen, and also share this...</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
You all know the truth many of you write of it too.  But then you turn around and deny it is happening infront of your own eyes.  o.O<br>
